content: I'm logged into the zoom call and it still hasn't started at 8:15. Should I bail or is this normal?
I will flag the text team to see if they know what's going on, but staff has been absolutely swarmed these last few days so it may just be a delay. Hang tight!
I flagged them but can you confirm which training you signed up for? Was it the persuasion text team training?

Sure: Harris For President Text Team

https://events.democrats.org/event/654680/
Trying to get to the bottom of this. Just to make sure, nothing has started and does it show "waiting for host to join"?
Correct, nothing has started and "waiting for host to start meeting"
If there's another one soon I can join that's fine, if you have a link!

After doing some digging, there seems to have been an error with Mobilize. The text team is no longer doing any training. That said, there is a new text-based team called the Persuasion text team that IS offering training. You can even do this one on-demand if you'd like, although they do have trainings on Zoom as well to sign up for. Check out this channel if you're interested: https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1298623273566732300
